{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"performance.now()","mdn_url":"/de/docs/Web/API/Performance/now","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Performance\"><code>Performance</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Eigenschaften</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Performance/navigation\"><code>navigation</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Performance/timeOrigin\"><code>timeOrigin</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Performance/timing\"><code>timing</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Methoden</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Performance/clearMarks\"><code>clearMarks()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Performance/clearMeasures\"><code>clearMeasures()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Performance/clearResourceTimings\"><code>clearResourceTimings()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Performance/getEntries\"><code>getEntries()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Performance/getEntriesByName\"><code>getEntriesByName()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Performance/getEntriesByType\"><code>getEntriesByType()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Performance/mark\"><code>mark()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Performance/measure\"><code>measure()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><em><code>now()</code></em></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Performance/setResourceTimingBufferSize\"><code>setResourceTimingBufferSize()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Performance/toJSON\"><code>toJSON()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Ereignisse</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Performance/resourcetimingbufferfull_event\"><code>resourcetimingbufferfull</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Vererbung:</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>Die&nbsp;<code><strong>performance.now()</strong></code> Methode gibt einen <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMHighResTimeStamp\"><code>DOMHighResTimeStamp</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> zurück, der in Millisekunden gemessen wird und auf fünf Tausendstel einer Millisekunde (5 Mikrosekunden) genau ist.</p>\n\n<p>Der zurückgegebene Wert stellt die Zeit dar, die seit&nbsp;<strong>time origin&nbsp;</strong>(der <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PerformanceTiming/navigationStart\"><code>PerformanceTiming.navigationStart</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> Eigenschaft und damit der Startzeit) vergangen ist. In einem Web Worker ist die Startzeit die Zeit, in der ihr Ausführungskontext (Thread oder Prozess) erstellt wurde. In einem Browserfenster ist es die Zeit, zu der eine Nutzerin zu dem aktuellen Dokument navigierte (oder die Navigation bestätigte, sollte Bestätigung notwendig gewesen sein). Folgende Punkte sind dabei zu beachten:</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li>In dedizierten web workern, die im <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>Window</code></a>-Kontext erstellt wurden, wird der Wert kleiner sein, als&nbsp;<code>performance.now()</code>&nbsp;in dem Browserfenster, aus dem der worker hervorging. Ehemals gleich&nbsp;<code>t0</code>&nbsp;dem Hauptkontext wurde dies in der Vergangenheit auf das heutige Verhalten&nbsp;geändert.</li>\n <li>In geteilten Worker oder Service Workern kann es passieren, dass der Wert im Worker größer ist als der des Hauptkontextes, da das Fenster nach den Workern erschaffen werden kann.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><em>t</em> = performance.now();</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beispiel","title":"Beispiel","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> zeit0 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> performance<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">now</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">machEtwas</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> zeit1 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> performance<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">now</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Der Aufruf von machEtwas dauerte \"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>zeit1 <span class=\"token operator\">-</span> zeit0<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">\" Millisekunden.\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p>Anders als andere Zeitmessungsdaten, die in JavaScript verfügbar sind (beispielsweise&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/now\"><code>Date.now</code></a>), sind die Zeitstempel, die von&nbsp;<code>Performance.now()</code>&nbsp;zurückgegeben werden nicht auf eine Auflösung von einer Millisekunde beschränkt. Stattdessen repräsentieren sie Zeit als Fließkommazahl mit einer Präzision von bis zu einer Mikrosekunde.</p>\n\n<p>Ebenso anders als&nbsp;<code>Date.now()</code>, wachsen die Werte, die von&nbsp;<code>Performance.now() </code>zurückgegeben werden immer in einem konstanten Tempo, unabhängig von der Systemuhr (die manuell&nbsp;eingestellt oder durch Software wie NTP ungenau geworden&nbsp;sein kann). Ansonsten wird&nbsp;<code>performance.timing.navigationStart + performance.now()</code> annähernd ähnlich zu&nbsp;<code>Date.now() sein</code>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"spezifkationen","title":"Spezifkationen","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Spezifikation</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Kommentar</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/hr-time-2/#dom-performance-now\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">High Resolution Time Level 2<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'performance.now()' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Empfehlung</span></td>\n   <td>Strengere Definition von Schnittstellen und Typen</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/hr-time-1/#dom-performance-now\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">High Resolution Time<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'performance.now()' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Empfehlung</span></td>\n   <td>Ursprüngliche Definition</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browserkompatibilität","title":"Browserkompatibilität","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect2\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Wir konvertieren die Kompatibilitätsdaten in ein maschinenlesbares JSON Format</a></strong>.\n            Diese Kompatibilitätstabelle liegt noch im alten Format vor,\n            denn die darin enthaltenen Daten wurden noch nicht konvertiert.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Finde heraus wie du helfen kannst! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect3\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Mobile</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Edge</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Grundsätzliche Unterstützung</td>\n   <td>20.0 <span class=\"inlineIndicator prefixBox prefixBoxInline\" title=\"prefix\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Vendor_Prefix\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">webkit (en-US)</a></span><br>\n    24.0 [1]</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/15\" title=\"Veröffentlicht am 2012-08-28.\">15.0</a> (15.0)</td>\n   <td>10.0</td>\n   <td>15.0</td>\n   <td>8.0</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>in Web Workern</td>\n   <td>33</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/34\" title=\"Veröffentlicht am 2014-12-01.\">34.0</a> (34.0)</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>now()</code>&nbsp;in einem dedizierten Worker ist nun unabhängig vom&nbsp;<code>now()&nbsp;</code>des Hauptkontextes.</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/45\" title=\"Veröffentlicht am 2016-03-08.\">45.0</a> (45.0)</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Android Webview</th>\n   <th>Edge</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n   <th>Chrome for Android</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Grundsätzliche Unterstützung</td>\n   <td>4.0</td>\n   <td>25.0</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td>15.0 (15.0)</td>\n   <td>10.0</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Nicht unterstützt</span></td>\n   <td>9</td>\n   <td>25.0</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>in Web Workern</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td>34.0 (34.0)</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>now()</code>&nbsp;in einem dedizierten Worker ist nun unabhängig vom&nbsp;<code>now()&nbsp;</code>des Hauptkontextes.</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td>45.0 (45.0)</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<p>[1] Windows Versionen von Chrome 20 bis 33&nbsp;geben&nbsp;<code>performance.now()</code>&nbsp;nur mit einer Millisekundengenauigkeit zurück.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"siehe_auch","title":"Siehe auch","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"http://updates.html5rocks.com/2012/08/When-milliseconds-are-not-enough-performance-now\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">When milliseconds are not enough: performance.now() </a>bei HTML5 Rocks.</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Beispiel","id":"beispiel"},{"text":"Spezifkationen","id":"spezifkationen"},{"text":"Browserkompatibilität","id":"browserkompatibilität"},{"text":"Siehe auch","id":"siehe_auch"}],"summary":"Die performance.now() Methode gibt einen DOMHighResTimeStamp (en-US) zurück, der in Millisekunden gemessen wird und auf fünf Tausendstel einer Millisekunde (5 Mikrosekunden) genau ist.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"performance.now()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"performance.now()","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"performance.now()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"performance.now()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"performance.now()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"performance.now()","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"performance.now()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Performance.now()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/api/performance/now","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/api/performance/now/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API Referenz"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/Performance","title":"Performance"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/Performance/now","title":"performance.now()"}],"pageTitle":"performance.now() - Web API Referenz | MDN","noIndexing":false}}